subject: Skiing
World Cup (Skiing)
Figure Skating
lead_paragraph: Maze beat Frida Hansdotter by 0.34 in a women’s World Cup slalom race in Levi, Finland, on Saturday, and the defending world champion Mikaela Shiffrin finished 11th.
